            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>UI is busier than Buffer</li>
                <li>Analytics are decent but not deep</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Budget-conscious posters covering 4+ channels.</div>
            <a href="https://publer.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="tool-cta-btn">View pricing →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">06</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">SocialBee</div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best for content rotation</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">$24<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">/mo</span></div>
              <div class="per">Bootstrap plan</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it delivers</h5>
