        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">07</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">Loomly</div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best for small teams</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
              <div class="price">$42<span style="font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-3);">/mo</span></div>
              <div class="per">Base plan, 2 users</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it delivers</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>Approval workflows built for small teams</li>
                <li>Post ideas and content prompts included</li>
                <li>Collaborative calendar that feels like Asana</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Overkill for solo posters</li>
                <li>Pricing scales fast with users and channels</li>
